Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.93,0:00:01.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.77,0:00:02.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.89,0:00:03.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That... that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.69,0:00:05.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What on earth is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.24,0:00:08.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Clea... ning...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.13,0:00:12.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How annoying!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.44,0:00:13.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This damn Trashbot!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.74,0:00:16.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Clea... ning... Clean... ning...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.26,0:00:17.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What on earth is happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.95,0:00:22.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you going to do with my conditions?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.10,0:00:25.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you worry about the safety of those hostages?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.42,0:00:28.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Money! Hurry up and prepare some money!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.57,0:00:30.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And don't forget the helicopter!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.80,0:00:35.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now the criminal who is inside the shopping mall
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.01,0:00:38.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}demands cash and a helicopter for running away.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.17,0:00:40.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad, a big incident!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.87,0:00:47.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma, you're in the Shopping Mall right now, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.78,0:00:53.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about? I... eh... school, I'm still in school!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.16,0:00:53.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.15,0:00:55.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No need to say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.30,0:00:56.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.19,0:00:57.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yesss~
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.56,0:00:59.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know you were there for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.10,0:01:02.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because you're already on TV!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.57,0:01:06.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh! They're recording me!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.49,0:01:09.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you understand? Hurry up and shoot some scoop photos for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.29,0:01:13.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just you say so - Geez!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.63,0:01:15.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Besides the helicopter for getting away...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.82,0:01:17.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}{\an8}Hurry up and provide me those things!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.08,0:01:21.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a scary face he has!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.65,0:01:25.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, Yuma! It's Numbers!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.79,0:01:28.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The criminal actually has a Numbers?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.66,0:01:31.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please let me pass, sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.67,0:01:32.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.87,0:01:40.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Numbers, confirmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.16,0:01:42.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, let the hunt begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.49,0:01:44.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.46,0:01:57.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let... let me pass!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.62,0:02:02.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh... what the heck is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.89,0:02:07.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shit! What happened to the money they promised me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.90,0:02:19.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.93,0:02:20.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.93,0:02:23.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.16,0:02:25.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Time stopped?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.76,0:02:27.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would such a thing happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.99,0:02:39.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's... going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.11,0:02:41.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.86,0:02:45.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell're you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.49,0:02:50.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am the light that illuminates the darkness \Nstagnating in the hearts of humanity...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.15,0:02:54.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People address me as the Numbers Hunter!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.78,0:02:56.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Numbers... Hunter?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.34,0:03:00.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then allow me to reclaim your Numbers!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.02,0:03:07.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How... how dare he do that to my friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.34,0:03:10.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to teach him a good lesson, Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.52,0:03:14.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... I mean Kaito-{\i1}sama{\i0}!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.67,0:03:15.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, then let's duel!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.32,0:03:18.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me tear up the darkness inside you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.26,0:03:20.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You... you said duel?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.68,0:03:24.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh. Numbers can only attach to Duelists.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.79,0:03:28.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so? Then this card... is known as Numbers?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.93,0:03:32.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you must have this kind of card too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.51,0:03:38.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Interesting! Then your Numbers... is mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.08,0:03:39.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Foolish!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.16,0:03:42.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then allow me to release you from your suffering!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.56,0:03:43.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.27,0:03:47.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duel mode, Photon Change!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.95,0:04:06.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, allow me to hunt your soul!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.86,0:04:10.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wa... wait! Can you let me pass by?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.46,0:04:13.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma, there is a duel on the top floor!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.67,0:04:15.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha... what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.62,0:04:23.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Whether it's rainy, or windy,\N or a cold winter blizzard, or the burning sun,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.76,0:04:26.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}they're all ingredients to color each day. \NDon't lose heart, will or love.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.86,0:04:29.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The kindness you gave me was strict,\N when we clashed I learned irritation.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.93,0:04:34.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It starts by recognizing our differences, dancing freely,\N the creation of Heaven and Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.27,0:04:41.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The truth is, I was lonely. Until I met you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.34,0:04:47.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I lied to myself that being alone was easier.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.12,0:04:54.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My favorite books and hobbies,\N they don't seem to match.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.52,0:04:58.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You were the only one to nod in agreement with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.73,0:05:01.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Happiness and sadness and anger and\N Do and Re and Mi and Fa and So and La and Ti and Do,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.53,0:05:03.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It doesn't work unless they're different,\N the harmony and the scenario.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.27,0:05:07.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No one is exactly the same,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.57,0:05:11.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}because that's the reason for living.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.61,0:05:16.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even if the sounds are dissonant from time to time,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.04,0:05:22.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}don't give up on the strength that will get you through.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.28,0:05:26.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When we reach the edge of the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.35,0:05:30.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}the view we see will be the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.42,0:05:33.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Whether it's rainy, or windy,\N or a cold winter blizzard, or the burning sun,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.33,0:05:36.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They're all ingredients to color each day.\N Don't lose heart, will or love.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.43,0:05:39.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}the kindness you gave me was strict,\N when we clashed I learned irritation.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.50,0:05:43.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It starts by recognizing our differences, dancing freely,\N the creation of Heaven and Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.40,0:05:56.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaito, who is collecting the Numbers cards, -->\N<--his goal for doing that is...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.22,0:06:01.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell {\i1}are{\i0} you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.99,0:06:05.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell are you!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.22,0:06:08.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a8}"Numbers 13: The Soul Hunter! \N Numbers Pursuer Appears!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.22,0:06:08.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that all the power of your Numbers offers...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.86,0:06:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Galaxy-Eyes Photon Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.12,0:06:14.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Photon Stream of Destruction!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.63,0:06:35.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Photon Hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.40,0:06:55.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The hunt for Numbers is completed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.01,0:06:57.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.28,0:07:07.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is... why the criminal...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.21,0:07:12.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Num... Numbers Hunter...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.17,0:07:14.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What... what did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.60,0:07:16.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Numbers Hunter?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.46,0:07:17.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.02,0:07:21.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.00,0:07:26.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Numbers was taken away!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.58,0:07:34.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.08,0:07:40.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's happening? That boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.03,0:07:42.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,LET'S GET HIM!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.57,0:07:44.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How... how did that boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.38,0:07:46.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did you get in?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.06,0:07:47.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Just be quiet!!...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.60,0:07:50.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W... wait!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.35,0:08:07.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Trash... trash... trash... trash...  ...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.28,0:08:36.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me hear... more screams!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.50,0:09:14.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More... more...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.81,0:09:21.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.74,0:09:28.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is the Numbers reclaiming going well?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.98,0:09:29.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.74,0:09:32.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's excellent.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.57,0:09:39.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That zealous duel of yours can definitely bring peace to the Heartland!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.18,0:09:43.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then how many Numbers did you manage to collect?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.42,0:09:44.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Orbital.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.56,0:09:45.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.70,0:09:50.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So far we collected 11 Numbers.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.35,0:09:54.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fantastic!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.58,0:09:56.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were able to collect that many within such short time period.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.82,0:09:59.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like I've made the right choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.04,0:10:02.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened, Kaito?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.62,0:10:04.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.11,0:10:08.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You seem to worry about the snatched souls, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.19,0:10:11.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.48,0:10:18.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With the science we have currently, we can only take away Numbers along with the holders' soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.84,0:10:21.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But no need to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.31,0:10:25.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People who were controlled by Numbers all were attached to evil forces.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.42,0:10:29.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those forces amplify their desires, so they all are bad people.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.53,0:10:32.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it true that if I manage to collect all 100 Numbers,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.18,0:10:37.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then Haruto... my little brother can go back to normal?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.70,0:10:39.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.46,0:10:43.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The only treatment to cure Haruto is to collect all Numbers.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.95,0:10:46.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now all you have to do is to believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.45,0:10:47.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No need to worry,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.26,0:10:51.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,your ambitious heart can will certainly touch Dr. Faker.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.47,0:10:53.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.57,0:10:57.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Continue your Quest for Numbers!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.31,0:11:03.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sooner you find them, the faster Haruto will recover.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.00,0:11:21.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How's the progress with the reclaiming of Numbers?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.80,0:11:25.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dr. Faker-{\i1}sama{\i0}, everything is going well.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.88,0:11:28.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so, then good!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.30,0:11:32.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to protect something important,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.20,0:11:34.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,people have to give up something in proportion as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.97,0:11:40.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like me. For the sake of protecting this world, I gave up the right to be a {\i1}human{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.97,0:11:45.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to protect Haruto, Kaito resigned to be a human as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.70,0:11:47.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Dr. Faker-{\i1}sama{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.39,0:11:52.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One day, I know there will be a messenger from the Astral World.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.49,0:11:58.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That day, that time... there's no mistake, that messenger shall come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.86,0:12:03.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,WE HAVE TO BEAT THAT PERSON UNTIL NOTHING REMAINS!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.81,0:12:07.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,AND SEND BACK HIS REMAININGS TO THAT WORLD!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.35,0:12:11.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OTHER THAN THAT, THERE IS NO WAY TO SAVE OUR WORLD!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.09,0:12:11.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As you wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.95,0:12:15.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here is the News Coverage of the incident in the Shopping Mall.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.40,0:12:18.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}{\an8}Like I said, you guys made a mistake!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.81,0:12:18.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The boy who was caught along with the bandit,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.09,0:12:22.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,accidentally appeared between the policemen and criminal...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.33,0:12:25.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you became the spotlight of my special features?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.97,0:12:30.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Somehow Yuma got mixed up in the crime scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.76,0:12:31.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But how did you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.24,0:12:35.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh, don't worry about those details.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.32,0:12:36.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.42,0:12:40.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma, do you need to tell her about Numbers?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.16,0:12:44.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you an idiot? My sister never allows me to duel!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.98,0:12:47.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can I tell her that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.21,0:12:47.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Wh... what?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.01,0:12:49.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh.... no... nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.53,0:12:50.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You! Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.73,0:12:53.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like that, I didn't duel!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.22,0:12:54.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Numbers Hunter...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.17,0:13:17.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.35,0:13:34.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.47,0:13:38.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haruto, how are you today?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.66,0:13:39.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.73,0:13:41.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.38,0:13:44.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is everyone laughing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.65,0:13:48.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need laughter...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.08,0:13:51.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All I need is screams...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.87,0:13:53.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...something that can comfort me...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.42,0:13:57.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For me... I need more, more screams!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.25,0:13:59.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haruto...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.27,0:14:05.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big brother... am I strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.20,0:14:09.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... you're just having a bad dream...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.18,0:14:10.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.43,0:14:13.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... a bad dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.54,0:14:19.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So don't worry. I swear I'll awaken you from that dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.69,0:14:27.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.91,0:14:29.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.64,0:14:33.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If besides me, there are other people collecting Numbers...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.98,0:14:35.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something about that Numbers Hunter, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.39,0:14:41.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does that mean, one day that Hunter will come after me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.98,0:14:45.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It won't take too long for that Hunter to find you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.51,0:14:47.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... maybe he already found you...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.41,0:14:50.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the... are you trembling?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.17,0:14:54.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then watch how I duel, and win in my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.17,0:14:57.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a bad feeling about this...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.85,0:15:07.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is a huge Duel square in the neighboring town!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.11,0:15:11.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice! Let's check that out on Sunday!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.72,0:15:15.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kotori, I'll let you witness my brigning it to 'em!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.05,0:15:17.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? If you can win, then why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.15,0:15:25.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! That's a close one!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.39,0:15:28.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I had decided to attack then...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.58,0:15:29.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Kotori?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.80,0:15:32.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, didn't you lose all your matches?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.12,0:15:37.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Bringing it to 'em means endless challenges!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.40,0:15:39.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The important thing is to never give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.40,0:15:41.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then when can you win for once?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.02,0:15:42.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, for sure!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.37,0:15:45.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma... looks like we should be on guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.97,0:15:48.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a bad feeling...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.89,0:15:50.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go again...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.77,0:15:51.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.34,0:15:53.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh nothing - nothing!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.64,0:15:56.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rain...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.36,0:15:58.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Darn it, it's raining... Let's go, Kotori!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.78,0:15:59.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.94,0:16:06.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are so slow, Kotori!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.78,0:16:08.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.59,0:16:13.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,KOTORI!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.54,0:16:21.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma, Yuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.71,0:16:26.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.29,0:16:30.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kotori!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.50,0:16:35.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What on earth is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.14,0:16:40.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... It's same as the last time!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.15,0:16:42.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This whistle...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.82,0:16:43.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.76,0:16:58.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.65,0:17:01.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you do all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.66,0:17:05.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now there is a special field within this area.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.87,0:17:08.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The time flow is slowed down to 1/10000 its normality.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.09,0:17:12.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's me, Orbital's power!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.78,0:17:17.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only those who hold Numbers can move freely in this area.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.70,0:17:20.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like you have Numbers too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.57,0:17:22.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Numbers... Don't tell he's...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.41,0:17:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the Numbers Hunter!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.64,0:17:27.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma, this man is extremely dangerous! Hurry up and run!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.46,0:17:28.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now you're telling me to run...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.94,0:17:34.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.34,0:17:38.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This duel anchor... until the Duel has an outcome...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.90,0:17:42.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...we cannot separate from each other!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.29,0:17:42.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.62,0:17:46.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, you cannot run away from this duel!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.40,0:17:49.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let the hunting begin, Numbers!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.35,0:17:51.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although I have no idea who you are...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.99,0:17:53.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I will accept your challenge!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.49,0:17:57.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma... I will help you in this Duel.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.82,0:17:59.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.30,0:18:00.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you tremble like crazy seconds ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.35,0:18:03.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never believe such things like instinct.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.17,0:18:06.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But... this opponent is an exception,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.62,0:18:08.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You cannot defeat him alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.93,0:18:11.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Is that guy that strong?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.69,0:18:12.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am afraid so.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.52,0:18:14.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He might be the strongest one you have faced so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.60,0:18:19.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... stronger than anyone I have faced...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.93,0:18:24.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you said that, then I am all fired up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.07,0:18:28.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't forget my goal is to become duel champion!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.14,0:18:34.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna bring it to 'im!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.87,0:18:37.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duel Mode, Photon Change!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.09,0:18:42.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.39,0:19:00.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}AR Vision - link established!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.56,0:19:06.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, let me hunt... your soul!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.32,0:19:09.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,DUEL!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.40,0:19:12.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will go first.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.05,0:19:15.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn, draw!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.05,0:19:19.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate the Magic card, Photon Veil, from my hand!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.27,0:19:26.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This card can return 3 LIGHT monsters from my hand to my deck,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.63,0:19:30.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and add 3 LIGHT monsters to my hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.23,0:19:32.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Exchanging 3 monsters...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.65,0:19:36.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I activate the Quick-play Magic card Photon Lead!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.58,0:19:42.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This card can special summon one LV4 or lower Light Monster, which was added to my hand from deck,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.69,0:19:45.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in attack position!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.59,0:19:47.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I special summon Daybreaker!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.23,0:19:57.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When this card is successfully special summoned,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.81,0:20:01.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can special summon another one from my hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.01,0:20:05.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come, another Daybreaker!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.35,0:20:09.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The newly summoned Daybreaker activates its effect!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.72,0:20:13.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I special summon Daybreaker once again!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.31,0:20:17.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Summon 3 monsters in a row?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.70,0:20:21.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no, all monsters on his field are LV4!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.95,0:20:23.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.92,0:20:26.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I overlay three LV4 Daybreakers,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.41,0:20:34.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I construct Overlay Network with these three monsters.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.71,0:20:36.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Xyz Summon!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.82,0:20:44.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come forth, No.10, White Knight Illuminator!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.10,0:20:52.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.53,0:20:56.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's able to summon Numbers in his very first turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.30,0:20:57.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not over yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.57,0:21:00.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate the effect of No.10 Illuminator!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.38,0:21:05.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once per turn, by detaching one Overlay Unit,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.79,0:21:10.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he allows me to send one card from my hand to the graveyard, and draw one card!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.45,0:21:15.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I activate the effect of Light Serpent which was send to the graveyard!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.86,0:21:18.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When Light Serpent is sent to my graveyard from my hand,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.95,0:21:21.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it can be special summoned to the field!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.74,0:21:27.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I normal summon Plasma Ball!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.72,0:21:35.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is more? Now he has three monsters...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.96,0:21:39.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How many monsters does that guy plan to summon?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.49,0:21:41.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.18,0:21:45.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I overlay the LV3 Light Serpent and Plasma Ball!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.04,0:21:50.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I construct the Overlay Network with these two monsters!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.29,0:21:51.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Xyz summon!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.66,0:21:58.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,come forth! No.20
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.29,0:22:08.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ant Soil Brilli-Ant!!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.74,0:22:12.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You gotta be kidding...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.39,0:22:15.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He summoned 2 Numbers in one turn?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.70,0:22:18.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now... let the hunt begin...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.36,0:22:25.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's start the Duel!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.03,0:22:27.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's this week's quiz!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.40,0:22:31.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Basically, how many monsters can you summon to the field in maximum?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.10,0:22:34.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,5 or 6?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.15,0:22:44.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Today's test is hard. I can't divide myself from pleasure and temptation.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.76,0:22:49.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I wanna watch TV when I get home.\N The recent anime are fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.87,0:23:04.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In any case, this test is hard. \NLanguage, Math and English are especially bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.37,0:23:09.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm only average at science and social studies.\N The only thing I'm good at is P.E.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.55,0:23:12.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}(Wait up, Baby!) For who's sake...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.25,0:23:14.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}(Is that, Baby!) ...am I remembering...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.69,0:23:17.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}(Just hold on, Baby!) ...the answer...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.25,0:23:18.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}(What are we!? Baby!) ...they wanted?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.92,0:23:23.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even if I write the correct answer on this paper,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.66,0:23:28.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}in one year, in ten years, will anything change?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.40,0:23:33.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The world I drew in the corner of my dreams,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.50,0:23:38.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}one day I will race through the open sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.28,0:23:43.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No one can blame this heart of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.15,0:23:48.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Nothing is really correct!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.00,0:23:53.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This guy is unbelievably strong!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.14,0:23:57.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me this guy's dueling is even above mine?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.75,0:24:00.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible!! I'm actually feeling fear to duel...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.37,0:24:03.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma, overcome that fear!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.47,0:24:06.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's work as a team in this Duel!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.32,0:24:09.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all... over now...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.82,0:24:10.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.50,0:24:16.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next  time on Yu-Gi-Oh! ZeXal!\N "Come forth, Galaxy-Eyes Photon Dragon!"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.97,0:24:18.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna bring it to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.95,0:24:28.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The answer is 5! When 5 monsters are assembled, there must be a great pressure, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.53,0:24:34.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to summon a bunch of monsters too, and use them to battle!

